"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20=
px 0;">This is the simplest way I&#8217;ve come up with to think about what=
 use cases currently make sense in crypto and which don&#8217;t yet, and th=
e simplest way to track progress in the space.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: =
rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">I=
t&#8217;s as much art as science, since developers will have to make a judg=
ment call on what users will care about more. Some will build products onch=
ain believing the trade-off has flipped in blockchains&#8217; favor, only t=
o realize that the benefits don&#8217;t quite outweigh the drawbacks.&#160;=
</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px;=
 margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>I think that&#8217;s what Dani Grant and Nick G=
rossman at USV were describing in their 2018 blog post, </span><em><a href=
=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/6a0f70c4-8cfd-42d5-a271-8b579680cf84?j=3D=
eyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=
=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-decoration: underline;">The Myth of the In=
frastructure Phase</a></em><span>: &#8220;First, apps inspire infrastructur=
e. Then that infrastructure enables new apps.&#8221;&#160;</span></p><p sty=
le=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0=
 0 20px 0;">It takes people being a little early and trying things that don=
&#8217;t quite make sense yet to show other developers which drawbacks need=
 to be attacked next.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-siz=
e: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>But the drawbacks </=
span><em>are </em><span>being addressed. During the bear market, crypto has=
 improved most of the drawbacks I listed above:</span></p><ul style=3D"marg=
in-top: 0; padding: 0;"><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px; mso-special-form=
at: bullet;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); fo=
nt-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left=
: 4px;">Slowness &#8594; faster L2s like Optimism, Base, zkSync and L1s lik=
e Solana, Aptos, and Sui</p></li><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px; mso-spe=
